### Invitation for Expressions of Interest (EOI)

#### Purchase/Lease of Industrial Space/ Warehouses in Greater Toronto

**Russian aerospace technologies services and research centre** became contracted for procurement services by **Public Works and Government Services Canada**, which has an ongoing HQ lease in Toronto.

**These procurement services involve the selection of a contractor who possesses capacity and experience in leasing landlord properties, which will then be located near other landlords were initially services were locate**.

*********

As of December 08, 2022, this Request for Proposal (RFP) is now officially open for submission.
Note that Public Works and Government Services Canada, as the contracting authority, is only receiving Expressions of Interest (EOIs) from interested parties, who then submit their expressions electronically at [https://buyapSSIPGP_info.energy)](https://canadabuys.canada.ca sponsored Photon.xtoolplane).
